tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE Demographics (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  location VARCHAR(255),
  population_size INT,
  age_distribution JSON,
  gender_distribution JSON,
  ethnicity_distribution JSON
);

CREATE TABLE population_demographics (
    population_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    location VARCHAR(255),
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    ethnicity VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE relief_efforts (
    effort_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    population_id INT,
    aid_type VARCHAR(50),
    amount INT,
    date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE ReliefEfforts (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  effort_name TEXT,
  organization TEXT,
  location TEXT,
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE PopulationAnalysis (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  analysis_date DATE,
  population_size INT,
  affected_groups TEXT,
  analysis_report JSON
);

CREATE TABLE demographics_data (
    demographic_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    age_group VARCHAR(50),
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    ethnicity VARCHAR(50),
    affected_population INT
);

CREATE TABLE relief_efforts (
    relief_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    location VARCHAR(100),
    organization VARCHAR(100),
    aid_type VARCHAR(50),
    funds_allocated DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE relief_needs (
    need_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    relief_id INT,
    need_category VARCHAR(50),
    quantity_needed INT,
    urgency_level VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE aid_distribution (
    distribution_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    relief_id INT,
    distribution_date DATE,
    distribution_location VARCHAR(100),
    quantity_distributed INT
);

CREATE TABLE PopulationDemographics (
	population_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	population_name VARCHAR NOT NULL,
	age_group VARCHAR,
	household_size INT,
	location VARCHAR
);

CREATE TABLE ReliefEfforts (
	effort_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	effort_name VARCHAR NOT NULL,
	effort_type VARCHAR,
	effort_description TEXT,
	location VARCHAR
);

CREATE TABLE ReliefWorkers (
	worker_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	worker_name VARCHAR NOT NULL,
	worker_type VARCHAR,
	skills VARCHAR,
	supervisor_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE ReliefSupervisors (
	supervisor_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	supervisor_name VARCHAR NOT NULL,
	supervisor_type VARCHAR,
	area_of_responsibility VARCHAR,
	location VARCHAR
);

CREATE TABLE ReliefSupplies (
	supply_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	supply_name VARCHAR NOT NULL,
	supply_type VARCHAR,
	quantity INT,
	unit_of_measurement VARCHAR
);
